<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirm Super Admin</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: none;
    }
    .button.deny {
      background-color: #dc3545;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Confirm Super Admin Status
    </div>
    <div class="message">
      <p>Dear {{creatorName}},</p>
      <p>You are being asked to confirm whether you approve the promotion of the user below to Super Admin:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{creatorName}}</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Please click the buttons below to approve or deny this promotion:</p>

      <a href="{{link}}" class="button">Confirm Promotion</a>
      <a href="{{link}}?confirm=false" class="button deny">Deny Promotion</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you did not request this action, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
